EN: Lightning is an electric current with high temperature.

ZH: 在夏季，会出现更频繁的闪电。
EN: During summer, there are more frequent occurrences of lightning.

ZH: 闪电能够点亮黑暗的天空。
EN: Lightning can illuminate a dark sky.

ZH: 闪电的速度非常快。
EN: Lightning is extremely fast.

